    <source src="https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3414580/extras/353dadfd4cd29b8239f0a4c3b1f12020.mp4?t=1777570176" type="video/mp4"/>
   </video>
  </span>
 </p>
 <ul class="bb_ul">
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Delve into a 90's FMV-inspired digital hellscape of dungeons and death with visuals, story and music from the creators of
    <strong>
     Home Safety Hotline.
    </strong>
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Survive the horrors with bloodletting solitaire gameplay from the veteran indie team behind
    <strong>
     Shadowhand
    </strong>
    and
    <strong>
     Regency Solitaire.
    </strong>
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
    Purchase upgrades from the friendly eye that watches you from the walls.
   </p>
  </li>
  <li>
   <p class="bb_paragraph">
